================================================================================
(X) Getting help
================================================================================

- Help is given in header files (.h extension)
- Source files (.cpp extension) may contain more information, usually geared
  more towards implementation
- "Main" source files (in /src/ with lower-case names) also contain help
- See the Makefile for available binaries

